## Quick Start

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone <repo-url>
cd {{project_name}}

# Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Run tests
pytest tests/
```

## Development

```bash
# Create a virtual environment
python -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate

# Install dev dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Run linter
ruff check src/

# Run tests
pytest tests/ -v
```

## Testing

```bash
# Run all tests
pytest tests/

# Run with coverage
pytest tests/ --cov=src --cov-report=term-missing
```

